{"id":32,"date":"2022-03-15T14:11:59","date_gmt":"2022-03-15T14:11:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.creativeschools.co.uk\/our-ethos\/"},"modified":"2023-06-26T14:21:29","modified_gmt":"2023-06-26T13:21:29","slug":"our-ethos","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/about-us\/our-ethos\/","title":{"rendered":"Our Ethos"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Vision<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"712\" height=\"701\" src=\"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/10\/Word-Art.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1030\" srcset=\"https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/10\/Word-Art.png 712w, https:\/\/leahall.fet.ac\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/6\/2022\/10\/Word-Art-300x295.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 712px) 100vw, 712px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Our vision for our pupils at Lea Hall Academy is to provide a safe environment, where children feel happy which enables them to learn and reach their full potential.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\"> SAFE    HAPPY    LEARNING<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Aims<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our aims are that all pupils who attend Lea Hall Academy:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Learn in an inclusive and nurturing environment.<\/li><li>Develop their independence to enable good choices for now and for the future.<\/li><li>Feel they have a voice and value the voice of others.<\/li><li>Have aspirations and an idea of how to achieve them.<\/li><li>Thrive both academically and emotionally\/socially.<\/li><li>Have a positive experience of school.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>View The Forward Education Trust&#8217;s <a href=\"https:\/\/fet.ac\/about-us\/ethos-vision-and-values\/\">Ethos, Vision and Values<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rende